&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, enhance, and maintain core People Airtable apps that support all aspects of the employee lifecycle, such as performance, onboarding, and employee data management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and architect new Airtable applications with AI and automation at the core, ensuring systems are intelligent, scalable, and adaptable as the company grows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Airtable Interfaces, Automations, and Scripting to create clean, efficient, and data-rich user experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Evolution &amp;amp; Enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain automations, integrations, and data flows between Airtable and tools like Greenhouse, Workday, Slack, and Google Workspace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take a pragmatic approach to problem-solving,&amp;nbsp; evaluating and recommending alternative systems or tools when they better serve People team goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use scripting (JavaScript or Python) and APIs to connect systems and optimize recurring processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously monitor system performance, usability, and data accuracy,&amp;nbsp; iterating to meet evolving business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with IT and cross-functional teams to align on architecture, data governance, and long-term tooling roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document technical logic and train stakeholders to use and maintain Airtable applications effectively. Promote Airtable best practices across the People team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Youâ€™re a systems-minded builder who designs with automation and intelligence in mind. You combine a product mindset with hands-on technical skill, and youâ€™re motivated by creating AI-driven tools that make work simpler, smarter, and more human for every employee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in systems engineering, internal tools development, or technical operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in leveraging AI to enhance systems and workflows&amp;nbsp; : you experiment, tinker, and have experience using generative AI to build real solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience building advanced Airtable solutions using interfaces, automations, and scripting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in scripting (JavaScript or Python) and integrating SaaS tools via APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pragmatic problem solver who evaluates the right system or tool for the job:&amp;nbsp; Airtable-first, but not Airtable-only.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with HR or People systems (e.g., Workday, Greenhouse, Slack, Google Workspace) preferred but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong data modeling and systems design abilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and documentation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive, collaborative self-starter who thrives in fast-paced environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
