&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Airtable is the no-code app platform that empowers people closest to the work to accelerate their most critical business processes. More than 500,000 organizations, including 80% of the Fortune 100, rely on Airtable to transform how work gets done.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Join DeepSkyâ€™s R&amp;amp;D team as a Product Designer and define the future of AI-powered superagents. Youâ€™ll drive the product design vision for our core agent interface, shaping how users interact with advanced AI to solve complex problems. This is a unique opportunity to lead design for a 0-1 product, influence go-to-market and growth strategy, and create delightful, accessible experiences that drive user adoption and retention. If you thrive at the intersection of technical systems, cognitive design, and product innovation, youâ€™ll find this role both challenging and rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and champion a comprehensive product design vision and strategy for DeepSkyâ€™s AI superagent capabilities and user experience&lt;/li&gt;
